svg.title: 2025-02-03-android-saadi88zar_blogfa-aggregate
svg.desc: This is a visualization of data relating to web browser page load performance.It consists of three items: metadata about the page being tested, a video screenrecording of Firefox and Chrome browsers loading the url, and a composite graphic of 11 dual bar charts tracking specific metrics collected during the page load process. The top bar chart grows up from a center line, and graphs metric values in milliseconds, and lower is better. The lower bar chart grows down and contains the relative standard deviation, as a percentage value 0-100
